{"tid":2420572,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"MOX 存款利率調整通知","createTime":"2021-02-24T04:15:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-24T04:17:03.000Z","uid":119933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a09f6c22127221deb494cb2611ac2bbb6faee97d","tid":2420572,"uid":119933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T04:15:42.000Z","msg":"Mox為你送上每日利息，你每天賺取的利息都以複息滾存 &ndash; 今天耕耘，為明天收穫更多。<br />\n<br />\n我們不時檢視市場環境。經過謹慎考慮後，我們決定調整存款利率。 由2021年3月1日起，0.65%年利率將適用於每位客戶總計50萬港元或以下的存款。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"280d531ba976eb1595044586a27a121c56c6a86d","tid":2420572,"uid":74901,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T04:17:03.000Z","msg":"係時候拎返啲錢出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}